data.title: B Green One Way Skysmoke + Incendiary Delay Setup
data.description: Here is a simple and effective setup to delay / disrupt the Attackers push into B Site.

data.title: A Rafters to A Site Incendiary
data.description: This Incendiary lineup is useful for stopping players on the attacking side from pushing too aggressively onto A Site and will also prevent players from taking the A Site ult orb.
